videos.description: Travis Etienne powers into the end zone in the first minute of the game to get the Tigers on the board.
videos.headline: Etienne finds the end zone for Clemson

videos.description: Isaiah Simmons intercepts a throw from Jawon Pass that he takes 27 yards for another Clemson touchdown.
videos.headline: Tigers with a pick-six in second quarter

videos.description: Clemson defensive tackle Dexter Lawrence gets into the end zone for the first rushing touchdown of his career.
videos.headline: Clemson DT trucks in for a TD

videos.description: Hassan Hall returns the kick 93 yards for Louisville's first touchdown of the day.
videos.headline: Louisville finally finds end zone on return

videos.description: Clemson head coach Dabo Swinney's son Will grabs a pass from Chase Brice and takes it into the end zone for his first career touchdown.
videos.headline: Dabo's son scores first career TD
